## 🔴 CRITICAL ISSUES (Must Fix Immediately)

### C1. Registration Flow Race Condition
**File:** `dashboard-react/src/pages/auth/Register.tsx`
**Problem:** If merchant creation fails after user registration, user is logged in but has no merchant. Still navigates to onboarding which will fail.
**Fix:** Don't navigate to onboarding if merchant creation fails. Show error page with retry option.

### C2. Email Verification Not Implemented
**File:** `backend-node/src/controllers/auth.controller.ts:62`
**Problem:** `// TODO: Send verification email` — Token generated but never sent.
**Fix:** Integrate email service (Resend/SendGrid/Nodemailer).

### C3. Password Reset Email Not Implemented
**File:** `backend-node/src/controllers/auth.controller.ts:325`
**Problem:** `// TODO: Send reset email` — Token generated but never sent.
**Fix:** Same email service integration as C2.

### C4. No Subscription Created with Merchant
**File:** `backend-node/src/controllers/merchant.controller.ts`
**Problem:** Merchant gets `subscriptionPlan: 'free_trial'` but no Subscription document created. Subscription page shows "No active subscription."
**Fix:** Create Subscription document when merchant is created, or have subscription controller fall back to merchant data.

### C5. No Rate Limiting on Auth Endpoints
**File:** `backend-node/src/app.ts`
**Problem:** Login, register, password reset are vulnerable to brute force attacks.
**Fix:** Add `express-rate-limit` middleware on auth routes.

### C6. Access Token in localStorage (XSS Vulnerable)
**File:** `dashboard-react/src/store/authStore.ts:37`
**Problem:** `localStorage.setItem('accessToken', accessToken)` — accessible to XSS.
**Fix:** Move to httpOnly cookie (already using refresh token cookie, extend to access token).

### C7. Payment Webhook HMAC Bypass
**File:** `backend-node/src/controllers/payment.controller.ts:110-142`
**Problem:** If HMAC is empty, verification is skipped. Attacker can send fake webhook requests.
**Fix:** Reject webhook if HMAC is missing or invalid. Never skip verification.

### C8. No Payment Integration for Subscriptions
**File:** `dashboard-react/src/pages/SubscriptionPage.tsx`
**Problem:** All subscription actions mark invoices as "paid" with `paymentMethod: 'manual'`. No actual payment gateway.
**Fix:** Integrate Paymob checkout for subscription payments.

### C9. PostMessage Wildcard Origin
**File:** `dashboard-react/src/pages/store-design/StoreDesignPage.tsx:133`
**Problem:** `postMessage(..., '*')` — any iframe can receive messages.
**Fix:** Use specific storefront URL as target origin.

### C10. No CSRF Protection
**File:** `backend-node/src/app.ts`
**Problem:** Cookies used for refresh tokens but no CSRF middleware.
**Fix:** Add `csurf` or custom CSRF token middleware.

