## 🟠 HIGH PRIORITY ISSUES

### H1. Subdomain Check Race Condition (No Debounce)
**File:** `dashboard-react/src/pages/auth/Register.tsx:118-122`
**Fix:** Add 300-500ms debounce before calling subdomain check API.

### H2. Subdomain Validation Blocks Submission When Pending
**File:** `dashboard-react/src/pages/auth/Register.tsx:157`
**Problem:** `subdomainAvailable === null` causes validation to fail.
**Fix:** Allow submission when null; handle server-side errors gracefully.

### H3. Image Reorder Breaks imagePublicIds Sync
**File:** `dashboard-react/src/pages/products/AddProduct.tsx:166-170`
**Fix:** Update both images and imagePublicIds arrays when reordering.

### H4. Upgrade Buttons in Settings Don't Work
**File:** `dashboard-react/src/pages/settings/Settings.tsx:686-695`
**Fix:** Add onClick handlers to navigate to subscription page or trigger upgrade.

### H5. Bank/Paymob Forms Don't Load Existing Values
**File:** `dashboard-react/src/pages/finance/FinancePage.tsx:29,35`
**Fix:** Fetch existing bank info and Paymob config on page load.

### H6. CSV Export Uses Wrong Key Name
**File:** `dashboard-react/src/pages/reports/Reports.tsx:313`
**Problem:** Uses `d.تاريخ` but data has `label` key.
**Fix:** Change to `d.label`.

### H7. Shipping Cost Hardcoded to 0
**File:** `storefront-next/src/app/store/[subdomain]/checkout/CheckoutClient.tsx:78`
**Fix:** Add shipping zones/rates system. Calculate based on address.

### H8. Quantity Can Exceed Stock
**File:** `storefront-next/src/app/store/[subdomain]/products/[slug]/ProductDetailClient.tsx:130`
**Fix:** Add `Math.min(qty + 1, product.stock)` check.

### H9. Order Creation Has No Rate Limiting
**File:** `backend-node/src/controllers/order.controller.ts`
**Fix:** Add rate limiting on checkout endpoint.

### H10. Inventory Race Condition During Checkout
**File:** `backend-node/src/controllers/order.controller.ts`
**Problem:** Two simultaneous checkouts can both succeed with last item.
**Fix:** Use MongoDB transactions or optimistic locking for stock updates.

### H11. Cancel Order Doesn't Refund Payment
**File:** `backend-node/src/controllers/order.controller.ts:353-405`
**Fix:** Initiate Paymob refund for paid orders when cancelled.

### H12. No Suspend/Activate UI in Super Admin
**File:** `super-admin-react/src/pages/MerchantsList.tsx`
**Fix:** Add dropdown menu with suspend/activate buttons.

### H13. No Coupon/Discount System
**Problem:** Order model has `discount` field but no way to create/manage coupons.
**Fix:** Create Coupon model, API endpoints, and checkout UI.

### H14. No Variant Support in Product Management
**File:** `dashboard-react/src/pages/products/AddProduct.tsx`
**Fix:** Add UI for creating product variants (size, color, etc.).

### H15. Forgot Password Page Missing
**File:** `dashboard-react/src/App.tsx`
**Problem:** Login links to `/forgot-password` but no route exists.
**Fix:** Create ForgotPassword page with email form.

### H16. Email Verification Page Missing
**Fix:** Create email verification page/route.

