## 🎯 Golden Rules

| ❌ Never | ✅ Always |
|---|---|
| Skip email verification | Verify emails before full access |
| Store tokens in localStorage | Use httpOnly cookies |
| Skip webhook verification | Always verify HMAC/signatures |
| Hardcode prices/currency | Fetch from config/API |
| Client-side aggregation for large data | Server-side aggregation |
| Leave TODO comments unimplemented | Implement or remove TODOs |
| Expose demo credentials in production | Use env flags for demo mode |

